# Protected branches (bundle)

![Stop](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Stop_sign_MUTCD.svg/240px-Stop_sign_MUTCD.svg.png)

**Never implement bundle features on `main`.**

Protected branch: **`main`**

Canonical spec: [branch-workflow.md](../../docs/workflows/branch-workflow.md) and [overlays/lsi/docs/workflows/branch-workflow.md](../../overlays/lsi/docs/workflows/branch-workflow.md) when present.

## Refuse feature work

On **`main`**, in Agent, Plan, Ask, and Debug modes:

1. **Stop** — do not edit `docs/`, `overlays/`, `snippets/`, `templates/`, or `examples/` for feature work.
2. Show the stop image and tell the user to check out `feat/<slug>` or `chore/bundle-<slug>`.
3. Docs-only exploration on `main` is allowed for `/opsx:explore` when not implementing.

## Verify branch

```bash
git branch --show-current
```
